replies.body:
If the Crit chance were the same gold worth of MR or armor it would have been SO much better. You know who stacked health and might get use out of the crit chance? Garen. Thats literally it.

And it could be ridiculously cost efficient. It was cost efficient purely by base stats by level 13 on EVERY CHAMP and it really should have been built as a 4-6th item.

I really miss it. My {{champion:86}} Garen will never be the same {{item:3070}}
